The '''''Encyclopedia of Genetics''''' ({{ISBN|0-12-227080-0}}) is a print [[encyclopedia]] of [[genetics]] edited by Sydney Brenner and Jeffrey H. Miller. It has four volumes and 1,700 entries. It is available online at http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/referenceworks/9780122270802.

